de.engehausen.treemap

Interface IWeightedTreeModel<N>

  • Type Parameters:
    N - the type of node returned by model.
    All Superinterfaces:
    ITreeModel<N>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileModel, GenericTreeModel

    public interface IWeightedTreeModel<N>
extends ITreeModel<N>
    A tree model which provides a "weight" for each of its node. For use with a tree map, the returned weight of a node must be larger or the same as the sum of all its children.
